sblkh - sandbox for linux kernel hacking

sandbox
 - scripts
 - doc
 - automated tests

tricks to debug kernel
 - printk
 - kgdb
 - dynamic debug
 - ftrace
 - ...

br2-external
 - br2 qemu defconfig
 - ccache
 - docker
 - out-of-tree driver
 - script to run qemu

gitlab CI
 - runtime tests
 - static analysis

